    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS. This example is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a 3.64 ratio limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term reliability, the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells, and the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates to mitigate floor fatigue. The VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals and a cryo-treated exhaust hub. Suspension geometry remains tight with fresh bushings, providing the tactile feedback these chassis are known for. It sits on staggered Style 67 wheels with plenty of tread. A true driver's car that has been maintained with technical precision.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
